links.title: Why These Social Media Stocks Are Trading Higher Today
links.description: Shares of several social media companies are trading higher in sympathy with Snap Inc. (NYSE: SNAP) after the company reported strong third-quarter earnings results. links.title: Pinterest jumps as analysts say buy after Snap earnings beat
links.description: Shares of Pinterest ( PINS) are on the rise on Wednesday after both Bank of America analyst Justin Post and Goldman Sachs analyst Heath Terry upgraded the stock to Buy following Snap's ( SNAP) earnings beat. Post reads the latter's better than expected quarterly results as another sign of a strong online advertising rebound, an opinion shared by his peer at Goldman.
